{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "不为人知的真相 第19章 4-1 各怀伤心事",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "迦道夫感激芬罗达告知实情。\\n对于芬罗达问自己是否想为了救席菈\\n而使用晓之圣片的提问，迦道夫流露出\\n悔恨之意并予以否认。随后，谢斯找到\\n芬罗达说想借他的秘术之力一用。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100046_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芬罗达",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_09_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100046_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "芬罗达。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_09_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100046_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芬罗达",
            "context": "是你啊，迦道夫。其他人呢？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_09_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "他们在外面讨论今后的事。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_09_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "尤蒂尔\\n似乎去了森林那边。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_09_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "芬罗达，\\n我由衷感谢你\\n详细告诉了我们真相。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_09_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "这样一来，\\n我就能将亚罗拉斯的遗志\\n传递给他了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_09_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100046_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芬罗达",
            "context": "我只是做了力所能及的事。\\n以我过去的所作所为来说，\\n这些连赎罪都算不上……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_09_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100046_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芬罗达",
            "context": "不知道尤蒂尔\\n是怎么看待这件事的。\\n希望他不要钻牛角尖才好……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_09_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "真相已经都告诉他了。\\n接下来就只能祈祷他自己\\n能找到今后的道路了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_09_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "芬罗达，关于刚才的事……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_09_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "你之所以会答应亚罗拉斯的请求，\\n应该也是出于\\n你为朋友着想的心意吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_09_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "将这份心意讲得更透彻些\\n不是更好吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_09_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100046_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芬罗达",
            "context": "不……这样就好。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_09_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100046_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芬罗达",
            "context": "因为我那时一心想要知道\\n龙化的奥秘，让其为精灵所用。\\n这是无法狡辩的事实……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_09_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100046_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芬罗达",
            "context": "席菈的状态……\\n似乎还是老样子啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_09_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "自那之后我已经尝试了\\n世间流传的各种治疗手段和法术，\\n没有一种见效。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_09_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100046_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芬罗达",
            "context": "是吗……\\n很抱歉我无能为力。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_09_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "别道歉。\\n你可是她的救命恩人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_09_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "对我来说，席菈就是我的救赎。\\n只要她能像现在这样活着，\\n我就已经……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_09_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100046_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芬罗达",
            "context": "迦道夫，\\n你应该知道晓之圣片吧。\\n你不想得到它吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_09_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100046_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芬罗达",
            "context": "只要利用圣片的力量，\\n应该就能改变因果，\\n让席菈的心恢复原样……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_09_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "对我来说……\\n这个梦太遥不可及了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_09_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "国破家亡，生灵涂炭。\\n都是我力所不及\\n才招致的后果……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_09_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "逃离祖国，我投靠了你，\\n只为拯救自己的女儿。\\n我……是个卑鄙小人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_09_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "看着心灵残缺的席菈，\\n我偶尔会这样想……\\n也许这就是我遭到的报应。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_09_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "我想让席菈恢复原来的样子。\\n这种想法日渐强烈。\\n但是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_09_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "若只为她一人使用\\n那无法驾驭的力量，\\n便等同于重蹈覆辙……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_09_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "这一点我无论如何都想避免。\\n我不能背叛因为我\\n而牺牲的同伴和子民……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_09_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100046_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芬罗达",
            "context": "活着这件事……\\n还真是不尽如人意呢——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_09_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100046_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芬罗达",
            "context": "从前和你还有亚罗拉斯\\n一起度过的那段辉煌岁月，\\n再也回不去了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_09_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_09_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100046_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芬罗达",
            "context": "抱歉……\\n最近我总是忍不住\\n沉浸在怀旧的情绪中……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_09_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "别放在心上。\\n每个人都有追忆往昔的时候。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_09_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "我有点担心他们……\\n稍微出去看看情况。\\n席菈，我们走吧……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_09_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "好……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_09_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100046_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芬罗达",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_09_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100046_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "……\\n芬罗达，\\n你们谈完了吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_09_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100046_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芬罗达",
            "context": "哎呀……是谢斯大人啊。\\n有什么事吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_09_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "是的，有一件事\\n想找你商量——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_09_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "我想借你拥有的\\n精灵秘术之力一用。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_09_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100046_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芬罗达",
            "context": "如果现在的我能帮上什么忙，\\n我很乐意效劳……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_09_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "十分感谢。此举是为了\\n应对今后可能发生的状况\\n而进行的“战力强化”。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_09_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100046_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芬罗达",
            "context": "嗯，这倒是无妨……\\n那我该怎么做呢……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_19_09_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}